title: Did AOC Say the Public Shouldn’t See 9/11 Photos Because They’re ‘Triggering’?
subtitle: Attributing questionable quotes to U.S. Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez is a preoccupation for some people.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: U.S. Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez said that the public shouldn't see photographs of the 9/11 terrorist attacks on the U.S. because they're "triggering."
